Posts.Content: No, It is not possible to not find cancer. My friend have this kind of problem with her first stage of cancer. She did her check up from three different GYNO. At first she got the same result may be because of GYNO or some other reason. Then she went to different GYNO & she was little clear than before. Finally she got the solution & she is taking care of her Cancer with good cancer center.
Posts.Title: Is it possible to not find cancer?
